snippet.title: Elements Destiny Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Elements Destiny is a retro-JRPG inspired by SNES era. It features an emotional story with a diverse cast of characters, a thrilling soundtrack with over 100 Tracks and stunning pixel art visuals.

Steam:  
GOG: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635500/Elements_Destiny/
Website: https://www.elementsdestiny.de/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GameEDofficial
